  "text": "For Western blot analysis, four groups of rat hearts (nϭ4 each group) were snap-frozen at the end of the treatment period. Frozen hearts were homogenized in ice-cold lysis buffer and subjected to SDSpolyacrylamide gel electrophoresis as described previously. [CITATION_1] The membranes were probed with anti-phospho-GSK3␤ (Cell Signaling Technology) (1:1000 dilution).",
